  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Direct acting antivirals offer a new opportunity to monitor the immune response in Hepatitis
      C infection. In this study cytokine markers will be measured during therapy up to time point
      SVR 12 an correlated to clinical Parameters and regular laboratory findings.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
